\multicolumn{2}{r}{} & & -10x & -35 \\ 
\cline{4-5}
\multicolumn{2}{r}{} & & (c+7-10)x & 0 \\ 
\end{array}
\]The remainder is $0$ if $c+7-10=0$, so $c=\boxed{3}$.

